  "detailed_description": "<h1>Feature List</h1><p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play over 100 games! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Downloadable wallpapers </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Full soundtrack and music player </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make gameplay simpler with Help and Hint functions!</p></li></ul></p><br><h1>Collector's Edition</h1><p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Includes 8 extra themes </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >18 Downloadable Wallpapers </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Music player </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1 more collection room</p></li></ul></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sort through a fun way to play hidden object games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358280/extras/c73b0b5817fde183d6ae3bf82ce45d86.poster.avif?t=1729639380\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358280/extras/c73b0b5817fde183d6ae3bf82ce45d86.webm?t=1729639380\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358280/extras/c73b0b5817fde183d6ae3bf82ce45d86.mp4?t=1729639380\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Clear out hidden items and trinkets in a new set of beautifully arranged in themes such as 50s Diners, Groceries, Fancy Jewelry, Science Laboratory, and many more!  Enjoy playing a variety of mini-games and collect little trinkets as you go along! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358280/extras/447c60114f1aa1c1d0ef071d02b58adb.poster.avif?t=1729639380\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358280/extras/447c60114f1aa1c1d0ef071d02b58adb.webm?t=1729639380\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358280/extras/447c60114f1aa1c1d0ef071d02b58adb.mp4?t=1729639380\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >So have fun, relax, and sort through so much stuff 2!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sort through a fun way to play hidden object games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358280/extras/c73b0b5817fde183d6ae3bf82ce45d86.poster.avif?t=1729639380\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358280/extras/c73b0b5817fde183d6ae3bf82ce45d86.webm?t=1729639380\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358280/extras/c73b0b5817fde183d6ae3bf82ce45d86.mp4?t=1729639380\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Clear out hidden items and trinkets in a new set of beautifully arranged in themes such as 50s Diners, Groceries, Fancy Jewelry, Science Laboratory, and many more!  Enjoy playing a variety of mini-games and collect little trinkets as you go along! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358280/extras/447c60114f1aa1c1d0ef071d02b58adb.poster.avif?t=1729639380\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358280/extras/447c60114f1aa1c1d0ef071d02b58adb.webm?t=1729639380\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358280/extras/447c60114f1aa1c1d0ef071d02b58adb.mp4?t=1729639380\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >So have fun, relax, and sort through so much stuff 2!</p>",
